# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EOL Project — Single Mono-Repo .gitignore
# Covers BOTH:
#   • Deep (2)/      MES (Phase2 backend + mes-frontend + POKA-YOKE)
#   • New folder (2)/  CMS (api_server + frontend + plc_monitor)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# CRITICAL: VIDEO FILES — NEVER PUSH
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Production recordings + cycle clips can be 100+ GB.  Defense in depth:
#   1. Block ANY video file extension anywhere in the tree
#   2. Block the well-known recording folders by name
#   3. Block per-camera log files (ffmpeg stdout/stderr)

# All video formats anywhere
*.ts
*.mp4
*.avi
*.mov
*.mkv
*.webm
*.flv
*.wmv
*.mpg
*.mpeg
*.m4v
*.3gp
*.ogv

# Recording folders
videos/
**/videos/
MES_Videos/
**/MES_Videos/
CameraCMS_Videos/
**/CameraCMS_Videos/
_pending_*

# ffmpeg per-camera logs (live recorder stdout)
_cam_*.log
_cam_*.log.*

# Cycle metadata CSVs (large, runtime-generated)
cycles.csv
**/cycles.csv

# Big backup zips at root
*.zip

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SECRETS / CREDENTIALS — NEVER PUSH
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.key
*.pem
secret*
*secret*
**/secret.key
**/.jwt_secret
credentials*
*credentials*

# Backend config files containing encrypted credentials
backend/users.json
backend/cameras.json
backend/plcs.json
backend/plc.json
backend/zones.json
backend/camera_config_bindings.json
backend/video_config.json
backend/shifts.json
backend/shift_state.json
backend/cycle_state.json
backend/cycle_state.json.lock

