**/venv/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
**/*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

